---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Tow Truck 10-Ton 2026: Heavy Capacity Recovery Financing',
  slug: 'tow-truck-10-ton-2026',
  excerpt: 'Finance 10-ton tow trucks for heavy recovery operations. 0% down payment, no age limit. Bus and truck recovery services.',
  date: '2026-01-09',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Specialized Trucks',
  image: '/images/blog/tow-truck-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['10 ton tow truck', 'heavy recovery', '0% down payment', 'tow truck Malaysia', 'bus recovery'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Specialized Trucks</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>10-Ton Tow Truck: Heavy Recovery</h2>

      <p>10-ton tow trucks handle heavy recovery. Buses, trucks, machinery. Major accident recovery. Industrial equipment transport. RM800-RM2,000 per tow. 15-30 tows monthly.</p>

      <h2>Bank vs. Us: 10-Ton Tow Truck Financing</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Feature</th>
            <th>Bank Financing</th>
            <th>Ing Heng Credit</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Down Payment</td>
            <td>10-20%</td>
            <td><strong>0%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Financing Amount</td>
            <td>Up to 90%</td>
            <td><strong>100% Full Loan</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Interest Rate</td>
            <td>4.6-6.0%</td>
            <td>Competitive rates</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Truck Age Limit</td>
            <td>Maximum 5 years</td>
            <td><strong>NO Age Limit</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Approval Time</td>
            <td>7-14 days</td>
            <td>48-72 hours</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>10-Ton Tow Truck Prices</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Type</th>
            <th>New Price</th>
            <th>Used Price</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Integrated 10-Ton Tow Truck</td>
            <td>RM280,000-RM350,000</td>
            <td>RM120,000-RM180,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Flatbed 10-Ton Tow Truck</td>
            <td>RM250,000-RM320,000</td>
            <td>RM100,000-RM150,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Heavy Recovery 10-Ton</td>
            <td>RM300,000-RM400,000</td>
            <td>RM140,000-RM200,000</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>0% Down Payment Benefit</h2>

      <p>Save your cash for operations. Keep RM12,000-RM40,000 in your bank. Use full financing for complete purchase. Add recovery equipment. Install safety systems. Keep working capital strong.</p>

      <h2>Heavy Recovery Income</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Service Type</th>
            <th>Rate</th>
            <th>Monthly Income</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Bus Recovery</td>
            <td>RM1,200-RM2,000</td>
            <td>RM18,000-RM30,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Truck Recovery</td>
            <td>RM1,000-RM1,800</td>
            <td>RM15,000-RM27,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Machinery Transport</td>
            <td>RM1,500-RM2,500</td>
            <td>RM20,000-RM35,000</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>No Age Limit Advantage</h2>

      <p>Used 10-ton tow trucks are powerful. Older trucks have capacity. We finance all ages. Banks reject trucks older than 5 years. We approve them. Save money on purchase. Get heavy recovery for lower price.</p>

      <h2>Business Setup Requirements</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Business Registration:</strong> SSM</li>
        <li><strong>JPJ Permit:</strong> Heavy tow truck license</li>
        <li><strong>Insurance:</strong> Comprehensive coverage</li>
        <li><strong>Contracts:</strong> Bus companies, truck fleets</li>
        <li><strong>24/7 Dispatch:</strong> Phone, GPS tracking</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Required Documents</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Business registration (SSM)</li>
        <li>Director identification</li>
        <li>Bank statements (6 months)</li>
        <li>Tow truck quotation</li>
        <li>Recovery contracts (if available)</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D1810 0%, #5D4037 100%); border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 24px; margin: 32px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
        <h3 style="color: #D4A574; margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">Ready for Heavy Recovery?</h3>
        <p style="color: #FAF3E8; margin-bottom: 20px;">Get your 10-ton tow truck with 0% down payment. 48-72 hour approval. No age limit on trucks.</p>
        <CTAButton href="/en/calculator" text="Calculate Your Payment" />
      </div>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <h3>Can I finance used 10-ton tow trucks?</h3>
      <p>Yes. We finance tow trucks of any age. No maximum year limit. Older trucks welcome.</p>

      <h3>What down payment do I need?</h3>
      <p>Zero. We offer 0% down payment. 100% full loan financing available.</p>

      <h3>How fast is approval?</h3>
      <p>48-72 hours for most applications. Complete documents speed up the process.</p>

      <h3>What income can I expect?</h3>
      <p>RM15,000-RM35,000 monthly depending on service type and utilization rate.</p>

      <h2>Start Your 10-Ton Tow Truck Application</h2>

      <p>Heavy recovery business awaits. Bus companies need recovery. Truck fleets breakdown. Machinery requires transport. Your 10-ton tow truck business is ready. Apply today.</p>

      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4A574 0%, #C49A6C 100%); padding: 24px; margin: 32px 0; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center;">
        <p style="color: #2D1810; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">0% Down Payment | 100% Full Loan | NO Age Limit</p>
        <p style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 8px;">48-72 Hour Approval | Bank Rejected? We Approve</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Get 10-Ton Tow Truck Financing" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 { color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  h3 { color: #8B6F47; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  p { line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  strong { color: #2D1810; font-weight: 700; }
  ul { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
  li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #D4A574; font-weight: bold; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  th { background: #2D1810; color: #F5F0E8; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; }
  td { border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; padding: 0.75rem; }
  br { display: none; }
</style>
